Package org.example.model.staging

Class WeatherDataTransform

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.example.model.staging.WeatherDataTransform
  • public class WeatherDataTransform
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents transformed weather data with standardized data types. This class is used to store weather data with standardized data types, facilitating data transformation and processing.
